🎉  Party Games — the ultimate collection of party games for friends and family!

No internet required. No accounts needed. Just grab your phone, gather your crew, and start playing.


🎭 CHARADES
Act it out — no talking allowed!

Choose from 7 categories including Movies, Animals, Sports, Disney, and more. Set your timer, hold the phone to your forehead, and let the chaos begin. A 5-second countdown gives the actor time to get into position before the word appears.


7 categories with 25+ words each
Adjustable timer: 30, 60, 90, or 120 seconds
Correct / Skip tracking with score summary
Haptic feedback on every action



🕵️ GUESS THE IMPOSTER
One player doesn't know the word. Can you find them?

Everyone gets a secret word — except the Imposter, who has to bluff their way through. Give clues, spot the faker, and vote them out before they figure out what everyone else knows.


7 categories: Food, Places, Jobs, Movies & Shows, and more
3 to 10+ players
Private pass-the-phone role reveal — flip to see, flip to hide
Player names saved between rounds



🐺 WEREWOLF
Social deduction at its finest.

Roles are secretly assigned — Werewolves, Villagers, and special characters. The app narrates each night phase, guiding players through the action without a dedicated moderator. Can the village find the wolves before it's too late?


Full night phase narration built in
3 special roles: Seer, Doctor, and Hunter
Automatic win condition detection
Role reveal screen at game end
5+ players recommended



